      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "dlg_d4_1",
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "上午，张奶奶说要洗个澡。卫生间地砖有些凉，浴缸边沿没有扶手，地上还湿漉漉的。",
          "layer": "essential",
          "duration": 4000,
          "typingSpeed": 30
        },
        {
          "id": "dlg_d4_2",
          "speaker": "spirit",
          "speakerName": "小精灵",
          "text": "洗澡是老人最容易跌倒的场景之一，尤其是有骨质疏松的张奶奶。水温、时长、防滑，每一样都不能马虎。",
          "layer": "essential",
          "emotion": "concerned"
        }
      ],
      "nextNode": "zhang_act1_d4_002",
      "tags": ["bath-safety", "fall-prevention"]
    },
    {
